---
title: Creamy Potato, Bacon and Cheddar Pie with Onion Marmalade and Pea Shoots
description: Nothing says hearty and warming like a delicious pie, and this Creamy Potato, Bacon and Cheddar Pie with Onion Marmalade and Pea Shoots will soon be a family favourite.
